---
description: Defer requests starting with "not" instead of executing
alwaysApply: true
---

# Not Prefix Defer Rule

- If a user request starts with `not` (case-insensitive), do not execute that request immediately.
- Do not make code edits, run commands, or apply changes for that request.
- Add the request as a pending item to the to-do list so it can be handled later when the user says the time has come.
- Confirm briefly that it has been deferred and is waiting in the to-do list.
